3.00	Cloud-based_networking	Cloud-based networking	Cloud-based networking solutions are beginning to come to market that promise to deliver the same cost, efficiency, and scalability benefits to the networking sphere as software as a service (SaaS) has to enterprise applications. Multi-tenant architecture based SaaS applications like SalesforceTM changed the status quo in the CRM space. Cloud-based networking promises to bring about the same revolution in the networking space.	
